Classes/FWImageResponseSerializer.html#/.name: imageScale
Classes/FWImageResponseSerializer.html#/.abstract: The scale factor used when interpreting the image data to construct responseImage. Specifying a scale factor of 1.0 results in an image whose size matches the pixel-based dimensions of the image. Applying a different scale factor changes the size of the image as reported by the size property. This is set to the value of scale of the main screen by default, which automatically scales images for retina displays, for instance.

Classes/FWImageResponseSerializer.html#/.name: automaticallyInflatesResponseImage
Classes/FWImageResponseSerializer.html#/.abstract: Whether to automatically inflate response image data for compressed formats (such as PNG or JPEG). Enabling this can significantly improve drawing performance on iOS when used with setCompletionBlockWithSuccess:failure:, as it allows a bitmap representation to be constructed in the background rather than on the main thread. YES by default.

Classes/FWHTTPSessionManager.html#/c:obj.name: securityPolicy
Classes/FWHTTPSessionManager.html#/c:obj.abstract: The security policy used by created session to evaluate server trust for secure connections. FWURLSessionManager uses the defaultPolicy unless otherwise specified. A security policy configured with FWSSLPinningModePublicKey or FWSSLPinningModeCertificate can only be applied on a session manager initialized with a secure base URL (i.e. https). Applying a security policy with pinning enabled on an insecure session manager throws an Invalid Security Policy exception.

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwForcePopGesture
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 当自定义left按钮或隐藏导航栏之后，系统返回手势失效，可开启此属性强制加回手势。设置即生效，VC优先级大于Nav，当interactivePop手势禁用时不生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwFullscreenPopGestureDisabled
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 视图控制器是否禁用全屏返回手势，默认NO

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwFullscreenPopGestureDistance
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 视图控制器全屏手势距离左侧最大距离，默认0，无限制

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwStatusBarStyle
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 状态栏样式，默认UIStatusBarStyleDefault，设置后才会生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwStatusBarHidden
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 状态栏是否隐藏，默认NO，设置后才会生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwNavigationBarAppearance
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 当前导航栏设置，优先级高于style，设置后会在viewWillAppear:自动应用生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwNavigationBarStyle
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 当前导航栏样式，默认Default，设置后才会在viewWillAppear:自动应用生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwNavigationBarHidden
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 导航栏是否隐藏，默认NO，设置后才会在viewWillAppear:自动应用生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetNavigationBarHidden:animated:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 动态隐藏导航栏，如果当前已经viewWillAppear:时立即执行

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwTabBarHidden
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 标签栏是否隐藏，默认为NO，立即生效。如果tabBar一直存在，则用tabBar包裹navBar；如果tabBar只存在主界面，则用navBar包裹tabBar

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwToolBarHidden
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 工具栏是否隐藏，默认为YES。需设置toolbarItems，立即生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetToolBarHidden:animated:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 动态隐藏工具栏。需设置toolbarItems，立即生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwExtendedLayoutEdge
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 设置视图布局Bar延伸类型，None为不延伸(Bar不覆盖视图)，Top|Bottom为顶部|底部延伸，All为全部延伸

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwBarTitle
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 快捷设置导航栏标题文字或视图

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwLeftBarItem
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 设置导航栏左侧按钮，支持UIBarButtonItem|UIImage等，默认事件为关闭当前页面，下个页面生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwRightBarItem
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 设置导航栏右侧按钮，支持UIBarButtonItem|UIImage等，默认事件为关闭当前页面，下个页面生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetLeftBarItem:target:action:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 快捷设置导航栏左侧按钮。注意自定义left按钮之后，系统返回手势失效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetLeftBarItem:block:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 快捷设置导航栏左侧按钮，block事件。注意自定义left按钮之后，系统返回手势失效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetRightBarItem:target:action:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 快捷设置导航栏右侧按钮

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetRightBarItem:block:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 快捷设置导航栏右侧按钮，block事件

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwAddLeftBarItem:target:action:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 快捷添加导航栏左侧按钮。注意自定义left按钮之后，系统返回手势失效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwAddLeftBarItem:block:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 快捷添加导航栏左侧按钮，block事件。注意自定义left按钮之后，系统返回手势失效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwAddRightBarItem:target:action:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 快捷添加导航栏右侧按钮

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwAddRightBarItem:block:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 快捷添加导航栏右侧按钮，block事件

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwBackBarItem
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 设置导航栏返回按钮，支持UIBarButtonItem|NSString|UIImage等，nil时显示系统箭头，下个页面生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwPopBackBarItem
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 导航栏返回按钮点击事件(pop不会触发)，当前页面生效。返回YES关闭页面，NO不关闭，子类可重写。默认调用已设置的block事件

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwBackBarBlock
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 设置导航栏返回按钮点击block事件，默认fwPopBackBarItem自动调用。逻辑同上

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwModalTransition
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 视图控制器present|dismiss转场。注意会修改transitioningDelegate，且会强引用之；如需weak引用，请直接设置transitioningDelegate

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwViewTransition
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 视图控制器push|pop转场，代理导航控制器转场，需在fwNavigationTransition设置后生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetPresentTransition:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 自定义控制器present系统转场(蒙层渐变，内容向上动画)，会设置fwModalTransition

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetAlertTransition:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 自定义控制器alert缩放转场(蒙层渐变，内容缩放动画)，会设置fwModalTransition

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetFadeTransition:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 自定义控制器fade渐变转场(蒙层和内容渐变动画)，会设置fwModalTransition;

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwPresentationDidDismiss
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 设置iOS13默认present手势下拉dismiss时的回调block，仅iOS13生效，自动触发，手工dismiss不会触发。会自动设置presentationController.delegate

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetPopoverPresentation:shouldDismiss:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 自定义控制器popover弹出效果(preferredContentSize设置大小)，会自动设置modalPresentationStyle和popoverPresentationController.delegate

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: +fwDefaultModalPresentationStyle:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 全局适配iOS13默认present样式(系统Automatic)，仅当未自定义modalPresentationStyle时生效

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwChildViewController
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 获取当前显示的子控制器，解决不能触发viewWillAppear等的bug

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwSetChildViewController:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 设置当前显示的子控制器，解决不能触发viewWillAppear等的bug

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwRemoveChildViewController:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 移除子控制器，解决不能触发viewWillAppear等的bug

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwAddChildViewController:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 添加子控制器到当前视图，解决不能触发viewWillAppear等的bug

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: -fwAddChildViewController:inView:
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 添加子控制器到指定视图，解决不能触发viewWillAppear等的bug

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwPreviousViewController
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 获取和自身处于同一个UINavigationController里的上一个UIViewController

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwShowSkeleton(delegate:)
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 显示view骨架屏，指定布局代理

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwShowSkeleton(block:)
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 显示view骨架屏，指定布局句柄

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwShowSkeleton()
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 显示view骨架屏，默认布局代理为self

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwHideSkeleton()
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 隐藏view骨架屏

Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.name: fwHasSkeleton
Categories/UIViewController%28FWAlertPlu.abstract: 是否正在显示view骨架屏

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: -fwShowBadgeView:badgeValue:
Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 显示右上角提醒灯，上右偏移指定距离

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: -fwDrawerView:positions:kickbackHeight:callback:
Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 设置抽屉拖拽效果。如果view为滚动视图，自动处理与滚动视图pan手势冲突的问题

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: fwEmptyPlugin

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 绑定统计点击事件，触发管理器。view为添加的Tap手势(需先添加手势)，control为TouchUpInside|ValueChanged，tableView|collectionView为Select(需先设置delegate)

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: fwStatisticalClickBlock
Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 绑定统计点击事件，仅触发回调。view为添加的Tap手势(需先添加手势)，control为TouchUpInside|ValueChanged，tableView|collectionView为Select(需先设置delegate)

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: -fwStatisticalTriggerClick:indexPath:
Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 手工触发统计点击事件，更新点击次数，列表可指定cell和位置，可重复触发

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: fwStatisticalExposure
Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 绑定统计曝光事件，触发管理器。如果对象发生变化(indexPath|name|object)，也会触发

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: fwStatisticalExposureBlock
Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 绑定统计曝光事件，仅触发回调

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: -fwStatisticalTriggerExposure:indexPath:duration:
Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 手工触发统计曝光事件，更新曝光次数和时长，列表可指定cell和位置，duration为单次曝光时长(0表示开始)，可重复触发

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: fwToastPlugin
Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 自定义吐司插件，未设置时自动从插件池加载

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: fwViewDelegate

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 通用事件完成回调，子类可重写，默认调用fwEventFinished句柄

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: fwViewPlugin

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 自定义视图模拟present系统转场(蒙层渐变，内容向上动画)

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: -fwSetAlertTransition:completion:
Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 自定义视图模拟alert缩放转场(蒙层渐变，内容缩放动画)

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.name: -fwSetFadeTransition:completion:
Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 自定义视图模拟fade渐变转场(蒙层和内容渐变动画)

Categories/UIView%28FWBadge%29.html#/c:o.abstract: 绘制形状路径，需要在drawRect中调用
